Only one account representing govt is required to deploy the contract,and same address is used as coin base.
The refugee can create account by enetering personal details.The account is automatically funded with 10000 tokens.
since no ether is available in the refugee account coin base is reuired to call functions that reuire gas.
refugee can log in to his personal account and use service by paying tokens.
refugee transaction can be viewd by entering refugee's register number.

ERC20 token was chosen for the project.
